genresAdvancedInfo.name: forro gospel
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Forro gospel is a genre of forro that incorporates Christian themes and messages into its lyrics. It is often performed in churches and religious gatherings and aims to spread the gospel through music. The sound is similar to traditional forro, but with a spiritual twist.
